{
  "stem": "19921.7",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I have this and this and that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I would like to have them and get back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And it started in 1991.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I just handwrit-- you know, hand write a letter to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Did-- didn't take it for-- just took it for granted, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "He would not even look at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And I sent it to him where I was born and everything else, what I did, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And went through about a week time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I get a real form to fill out, and my father's name, my mother's name, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And give him everything in detail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And sure enough, I got all my medals which I received during the war here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And it lasted from 1992 to 1994.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "The last one was in 1994.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "So I got everything back through that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What else could I add?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we covered everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's absolutely very important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I urge everybody, no matter how hard it is, we have to tell it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There are not too many of us left, and whoever is left is over 70 years old.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, thank God I'm still can do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even if I had a bypass already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I still can do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as long as-- as my mind is here, this mouth will talk about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was my pleasure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it was my pleasure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I was approached by the Spielberg Foundation through the Jewish War Veterans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was my pleasure to be here with you, and I thank you all of them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All of you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we do the photographs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
